<glossary>
<definition id="fs-id1172100556199">
<term>destructive interference for a single slit</term>
<meaning id="fs-id1172100511591">occurs when the width of the slit is comparable to the wavelength of light illuminating it</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-id1172100537220">
<term>diffraction</term>
<meaning id="fs-id1172100742529">bending of a wave around the edges of an opening or an obstacle</meaning>
</definition>
</glossary>

